title: WebDrive32 V11.00.2835 32-bit
description:
WebDrive32 V11.00.2835 - 32-bit version!

File access client that maps drive letters to FTP, WebDAV, SFTP and cloud servers.
WebDrive provides FTP Client capabilities without running a separate FTP software application.
Using the familiar interface of a drive letter, WebDrive enables you to store and edit files on FTP, SFTP and WebDAV servers as easily as you edit files on your desktop.
WebDrive also maps network drives to popular cloud storage services.
For activation of the program, read the .txt file.


Just have FUN.
